Meta: _et_pb_old_content:
YJX silicone hose kit connect the turbocharger outlet to the charge cooler inlet and the charge cooler to the engine manifold. Increases the power available from a given engine displacement and also forms a major part of engine control strategy aimed at meeting stringent exhaust gas emission regulations.

For superior connection between engine mounted charge air system components, YJX Silicone Hose is also ideal for handling slight misalignments and isolating vibration between hose ends.

YJX Silicone Hoses are constructed with reinforced Aramid and are used by professionals in industries such as high performance racing vehicles, commercial truck and bus, Marine, agricultural and off highway vehicles, turbo diesel, and general manufacturing industries.
